subject: Motorcycles, Motor Bikes and Motorscooters
lead_paragraph: Nate Adams wrapped up his second consecutive Dew Cup title yesterday, winning the Freestyle Motocross championship with a victory in the AST Dew Tour Toyota Challenge in Salt Lake City. On his first run, Adams pulled a back flip on a 95-foot gap, giving him a 93.33 score, good enough for the victory.
